<section id="about" class="fade-in">
  <span class="sec-lbl" id="lAbout">About Maharashtra</span>
  <h2 class="sec-title" id="aboutTitle">Land of <em>Warriors & Visionaries</em></h2>
  <p class="sec-body" id="aboutBody">Maharashtra, India's economic powerhouse, is a state of unparalleled dynamism blending history, culture, commerce and natural beauty. Home to Mumbai, the City of Dreams and India's financial capital, Maharashtra pulses with the energy of millions pursuing aspirations. From the majestic Ajanta-Ellora caves carved by ancient artisans to the historic forts of Maratha warriors, from the bustling Arabian Sea coastline to the verdant Western Ghats, Maharashtra showcases India's complete character. A land that has nurtured saints and philosophers, kings and entrepreneurs, artists and innovators, Maharashtra continues to lead India's progress. Known for its Marathi culture, Bollywood entertainment, thriving commerce, intellectual movements, and spiritual significance, Maharashtra represents the modern face of India while honoring its glorious past.</p>
</section>

