  <p class="sec-body" id="weatherNote" style="margin-bottom:0">Maharashtra experiences monsoon (June-September), hot summers (March-May), and pleasant winters (October-February). October to February offers ideal weather across the state for all outdoor activities and sightseeing.</p>
